opy, tighter\nconstraints can be placed on nuclear and particle astrophysics. ABRIDGED\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Jan 2004 17:42:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Jun 2004 20:02:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
